---
title: Creamy Coconut Caribbean Chicken with Rapid Rice, Rainbow Slaw & Peanuts
description: Caribbean spice is such a party for your mouth, we had to step up every element of this lively dish. From rainbow
slaw to crunchy peanuts, each colourful bite is a delight
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6499241e9d9349a5ae8c3592-1c9354ba.jpeg
